    <item>
      <title>保守党民意调查显示改革面临威胁，苏纳克提议为养老金领取者减税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/sunak-offers-pensioners-tax-cut-as-tory-poll-shows-reform-threat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[如果他的保守党打破胜局并赢得大选，总理里希·苏纳克将向养老金领取者承诺减税，这是试图支撑核心选票的最新策略，因为内部民意调查显示，由于保守党的复兴，保守党可能会失去 100 多个席位。右翼英国改革党。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/sunak-offers-pensioners-tax-cut-as-tory-poll-shows-reform-threat</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 21:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国马克龙在德国访问时再次呼吁“购买欧洲产品”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/france-s-macron-renews-calls-to-buy-european-on-germany-visit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总统马克龙表示，面对来自美国和中国日益激烈的竞争，欧盟必须停止天真，并再次呼吁在国防等关键领域采取“购买欧洲”战略。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/france-s-macron-renews-calls-to-buy-european-on-germany-visit</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 18:38:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普历史性的结案陈词将是“两个案件的故事”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/trump-s-historic-closing-arguments-will-be-a-tale-of-two-cases</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 封口费案的纽约陪审团在经过一周的休庭后重返法庭进行结案陈词，为历史性的审议奠定基础。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/trump-s-historic-closing-arguments-will-be-a-tale-of-two-cases</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 18:00:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯塔默和苏纳克互相嘲笑，对手瞄准目标选民</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/starmer-and-sunak-trade-jibes-as-rivals-zone-in-on-target-voters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[反对党工党领袖凯尔·斯塔默(Keir Starmer)嘲笑了里希·苏纳克(Rishi Sunak)的计划，即如果他的保守党继续掌权，就恢复英国年轻人的国民服役计划，因为竞争对手利用英国银行假日在两个领域进行竞选活动，这突显了他们在7月4日的选举中面临的截然不同的挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/starmer-and-sunak-trade-jibes-as-rivals-zone-in-on-target-voters</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 17:30:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拉脱维亚希望“无人机军队”支持工业和国防</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/latvia-wants-drone-army-to-bolster-industry-national-defense</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拉脱维亚表示，希望建立一支“无人机军队”，作为促进当地国防工业生产和加强波罗的海地区军事能力的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/latvia-wants-drone-army-to-bolster-industry-national-defense</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 17:06:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰陆军参谋长准备好接受可能的法国军事训练员</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/ukraine-army-chief-ready-for-possible-french-military-trainers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰总司令亚历山大·西尔斯基表示，乌克兰正在为法国军事教官可能的首次访问做准备，政府要求北约盟国帮助训练基辅军队以对抗俄罗斯的入侵。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/ukraine-army-chief-ready-for-possible-french-military-trainers</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 16:25:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>匈牙利否决乌克兰武器援助 欧盟国家愤怒</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/eu-nations-fume-over-hungary-s-vetoes-of-ukraine-weapons-aid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于乌克兰军队正在努力抵御俄罗斯的攻击，匈牙利拒绝向乌克兰提供超过 65 亿欧元（71 亿美元）的急需军事援助，这让欧盟成员国越来越恼火。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/eu-nations-fume-over-hungary-s-vetoes-of-ukraine-weapons-aid</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 13:59:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列空袭和埃及警卫死亡加剧紧张局势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/israel-egypt-troops-exchange-fire-in-gaza-says-israeli-media</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一，一名埃及士兵在加沙边境口岸与以色列军队的冲突中丧生，周日，以色列对流离失所者营地发动空袭，造成至少 40 名巴勒斯坦人死亡，进一步加剧了以色列与哈马斯战争引发的地区紧张局势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/israel-egypt-troops-exchange-fire-in-gaza-says-israeli-media</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 13:55:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>世界上任职时间最长的央行行长将在罗马尼亚获得新任期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/world-s-longest-serving-central-bank-chief-to-get-new-term-in-romania</link>
      <description><![CDATA[世界上任职时间最长的央行行长罗马尼亚穆古尔·伊萨雷斯库 (Mugur Isarescu) 即将获得新的五年任期确认，议员们寻求在 6 月底之前就延长任期进行投票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/world-s-longest-serving-central-bank-chief-to-get-new-term-in-romania</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 13:26:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西央行行长罗伯托·坎波斯·内托称通胀预测将改善</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/brazil-analysts-see-faster-inflation-into-2026-as-outlook-dims</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西央行行长表示，消费者价格预测将有所改善，此前一项受到密切关注的调查显示，经济学家将 2024-2026 年通胀预期上调至进一步高于目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/brazil-analysts-see-faster-inflation-into-2026-as-outlook-dims</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 11:57:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
